parent1.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with flaming feathers in the style of surrealism. It is soaring above the rooftops in an ancient city on a stormy day, scattering embers from its wings, amidst an environment of twisting spires and floating lanterns.

parent2.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with iridescent feathers in the style of Art Nouveau. It flares its wings on the verdant meadow in the enchanted forest on a misty morning, soaring gracefully above a carpet of blooming wildflowers, amidst ancient, towering trees with twisted branches adorned with glowing runes.

offspring.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with radiant feathers in the style of abstract expressionism. It perches on the edge of a craggy cliff overlooking a vast desert under a twilight sky, casting a warm glow from its wings, amidst a landscape of wind-carved rock formations and floating glass orbs.
